  "id": "019d286a-f2d8-78b2-92cd-69e959ce1247",
  "content": "## Quick Start\n\n### Option 1: Devcontainer (recommended)\n\nOpen in GitHub Codespaces, VS Code Dev Containers, or DevPod:\n\n[![Open in GitHub Codespaces](https://github.com/codespaces/badge.svg)](https://codespaces.new/anthropics/corvia-workspace)\n\n\n### Option 2: Local\n\n```bash\ngit clone https://github.com/anthropics/corvia-workspace\ncd corvia-workspace\ncorvia workspace init    # clones repos, provisions Ollama\ncorvia workspace ingest  # indexes both repos (or use pre-ingested knowledge)\ncorvia serve --mcp &     # start server\ncorvia search \"how does chunking work\"\n```\n",
